law.catch_line: Transaction of business by foreign limited liability company.
law.text: A foreign limited liability company qualified to transact business in this Commonwealth is subject to KRS 14A.6-010.
law.history: Repealed and reenacted 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 151, sec. 79, effective January 1, 2011. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 389, sec. 77, effective July 15, 1994.
